Firearm thinks so, because he heard Spears call for Prebon. But its not 
definite yet. I think the Trainers are on their way.

::Ramulus/Rust::

Ramulus walks over to the nearest working console, the only one in the room, 
and possibly in the entire Ark, looking at the scanner reports. He frowns as 
he sees a few Maximals heading toward the Ark.

"Aproaching Maximals," he says into his comm, "The Ark isn't very safe right 
now. There is a faction with a mind controll chip warring with us. If you 
wish to station here, you need to have the anti-chip. I have a few spares if 
you want them."
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Rust nods, marching after Dinotron.
